gets pirated.

00:06:24.900 --> 00:06:28.290
Hollywood and Congress derived this number
mathematically

00:06:28.290 --> 00:06:31.540
back when they last sat down to improve copyright
damages and

00:06:31.540 --> 00:06:33.500
and made this law.

00:06:33.500 --> 00:06:35.440
Some people think this number's a little bit
large

00:06:35.440 --> 00:06:38.590
but copyright mathematicians who are media
lobby experts

00:06:38.590 --> 00:06:42.080
are merely surprised that it doesn't get compounded
for inflation every year.

00:06:42.080 --> 00:06:43.080
