00:10:35.170 --> 00:10:41.350
Year Zero is the story of vast alien civilization
that is so into human pop music

00:10:41.350 --> 00:10:44.449
that they inadvertently commit the biggest
copyright infringements

00:10:44.449 --> 00:10:49.069
since the Big Bang, thereby bankrupting the
entire universe.

00:10:49.069 --> 00:10:53.410
All the wealth in our universe is owed to
