00:10:58.939 --> 00:11:04.009
You will all be delighted to know, I hope,
that the book is about two-thirds set in present

00:11:04.009 --> 00:11:08.399
day New York,
the rest is rambling across many galaxies

00:11:08.399 --> 00:11:12.149
and so forth in the way that we like to do
in science fiction.

00:11:12.149 --> 00:11:16.740
Now the aliens are in trouble because for
reasons that are baked deep

00:11:16.740 --> 00:11:19.921
into the storyline--and we'll all just save
a ton of time

00:11:19.921 --> 00:11:23.300
by suspending our disbelief on this point
for one moment--

00:11:23.300 --> 00:11:26.399
but for reasons that are baked deep into the
storyline,

00:11:26.399 --> 00:11:31.500
they are obligated to honor our copyright
laws.

00:11:31.500 --> 00:11:35.779
And they're also obligated to pay the fines
and penalties

00:11:35.779 --> 00:11:41.759
that are associated with our copyright laws
which they have violated in an unbelievably

00:11:41.759 --> 00:11:43.649
big way.

00:11:43.649 --> 00:11:47.910
And this is a problem because to quote
the most authoritative source on this subject

00:11:47.910 --> 00:11:55.490
