American copyright laws are, quote "the most

00:11:55.490 --> 00:11:59.249
cynical, predatory,
lopsided, and shameless money grubbing copyright

00:11:59.249 --> 00:12:03.010
laws written by any society
anywhere in the universe since the dawn of

00:12:03.010 --> 00:12:04.010
Time itself."

00:12:04.010 --> 00:12:08.889
Now that's not my opinion, that's the opinion
of one of the aliens in my book.

00:12:08.889 --> 00:12:12.020
[laughter]
