00:12:29.290 --> 00:12:35.170
the maximum fine for drunk driving is 1/300th
of that amount.

00:12:35.170 --> 00:12:39.699
Which makes sense if, and only if, you believe
that while drunk driving does indeed have

00:12:39.699 --> 00:12:45.399
terrible consequences, music piracy--again
quoting my authoritative source--

00:12:45.399 --> 00:12:50.499
leads quickly to meth addiction, cannibalism,
and societal collapse.

00:12:50.499 --> 00:12:55.470
Which is presumably what Congress was thinking
when they passed that rather crazy law.

00:12:55.470 --> 00:13:02.240
So, what happens in the book is that a self-appointed
alien delegation comes to earth

00:13:02.240 --> 00:13:07.450
to try to fix this terrible situation and
they quickly establish that the only way

00:13:07.450 --> 00:13:16.490
they can do this is to reverse this complex
thicket of laws and international treaties

00:13:16.490 --> 00:13:19.209
that literally go back centuries.

00:13:19.209 --> 00:13:22.470
And they quickly determine that the only way
they can do this

00:13:22.470 --> 00:13:29.610
is to recruit a very very powerful human ally
to help them navigate human society

00:13:29.610 --> 00:13:31.959
and help them achieve this almost impossible
task.

00:13:31.959 --> 00:13:35.050
