and he says:

00:18:22.240 --> 00:18:23.240
[Begins reading from Year Zero]

00:18:23.240 --> 00:18:25.750
"Soon I was down on the icy bustling streets.

00:18:25.750 --> 00:18:29.320
New York in February is New York at its worst,
unless you count those

00:18:29.320 --> 00:18:33.440
hundred-degree August weekends when everybody's
off at the Hamptons but you."--there's a lot

