their music from the

00:22:44.480 --> 00:22:45.580
Internet.

00:22:45.580 --> 00:22:50.929
And I think that is more to blame for the
piracy phenomena that followed than anything

00:22:50.929 --> 00:22:55.490
else
and so essentially what happened was in late

00:22:55.490 --> 00:23:00.360
1998, the first mass market mp3 player, the
Diamond Multimedia Rio,

00:23:00.360 --> 00:23:03.010
