00:23:07.490 --> 00:23:10.380
around on
bended knee to the music labels , hoping to

00:23:10.380 --> 00:23:11.769
get licenses.

00:23:11.769 --> 00:23:15.290
And I knew it was going to be bad when, within
thirty days

00:23:15.290 --> 00:23:21.700
