00:24:08.820 --> 00:24:14.880
And so you had this almost five year period
when this radically useful and fabulous and

00:24:14.880 --> 00:24:19.919
fascinating and flexible format came out and
the labels were simply not

00:24:19.919 --> 00:24:25.940
selling that . During that interim, it basically
amounted to a training period, which lasted

00:24:25.940 --> 00:24:28.639
about five years,
