very deeply baked I think into social norms,

00:24:52.159 --> 00:24:55.259
social norm practices,
and the music industry is still paying the

00:24:55.259 --> 00:24:56.679
price for that.

00:24:56.679 --> 00:25:02.639
What's very different today is that the labels
are willing to license, so there is much more

00:25:02.639 --> 00:25:06.250
a proliferation
of services that are out there.

00:25:06.250 --> 00:25:12.549
I think that a lot of pretty inventive services
that really could

00:25:12.549 --> 00:25:17.580
